 ICE CREAM WITH TRUFFLES 

00:00:20.430 --> 00:00:29.140
 Ingredients: - 900 g Milk - 50 g Sugar - 75 g Sosa Liquid Glucose - 100 g ProCrema 100 Cold Sosa - 50 g Glycerin Sosa - 50 g Fresh Truffles - 2 g Salt 

00:00:36.310 --> 00:00:50.600
 Mix solid ingredients and liquid ingredients separately. 

00:00:54.660 --> 00:01:00.790
 In a container, pour both mixtures and blend with a blender to obtain a perfectly homogeneous paste. 

00:01:04.430 --> 00:01:07.560
 Let stand in refrigerator for 3 hours. 

